courses.learning_outcomes:
By the end of the course, the student will be expected to:

1. Demonstrate a fundamental understanding of the compositional techniques introduced in the course;
2. Demonstrate creativity and originality in their own works, and the progressive development of a personal style;
3. Express self-reflective and informed judgments about their own compositions, compositional approaches and

creative ideas;
4. Have built a portfolio of compositions for small instrumental ensembles.

